snippet.title: Rubber Ducky Massacre - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description: Play my newest game, Rubber Ducky Massacre, online at http://duckgame.xyz/ (The game was tested on Google Chrome, so play it in that if you want the best experience. Also, it doesn't work on mobile, sorry about that.)
